						<div class="postbody">A followup with the Hyperkin, when testing at 20Hz the output values seem to be the same, rather than 1/3. I suppose with the optical mouse it has its own internal update, and maintains a &quot;current speed&quot; that it reports when you poll it? So for that one I suppose &quot;inches per second&quot; would be a better description.</div>

